# 14. Guiding Principle

Whenever a new feature is proposed, ask:

> **Does this change alter the physics engine or merely interpret its output?**

If it alters the physics engine,

it belongs in a future PANDA release.

If it interprets the output,

it belongs in PANDAEX.

